bio: Anish is a seasoned technologist with application development, system administration and architecture experience in building & transforming enterprise solutions in Telecom, Pension, Logistics and E-commerce domain. name: Tarun R Jain
bio: I am Tarun Jain, currently working as a DevRel and Data Scientist at AI Planet, a Belgium-based AI startup. I also talk at workshops that are organized at IITs as a contract of being Community Lead at Embedchain.ai. So far I have delivered 4 talks as the Community lead at - NSIT, IIT Bombay, IIT Ropar, and IIT Delhi. I was also part of Google Summer of Code 2023 at caMicroscope. I have been organizing workshops and AI/ML talks for over 1.5+ years as a Pie & AI Bangalore Ambassador at DeepLearningAI. This eventually led to the path of becoming a GDE in ML. I joined the Google Developer Experts program in October 2023. In my free time, I watch Anime and read Manga- One Piece being my favorite.
